%# Phases typiques des projets

^une vie // {"headword":"vie","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
~? **Phases** dans la **vie d'un projet** :
-initialisation
^lancer // {"headword":"lancer","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
-lancement
^une conception // {"headword":"conception","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-conception
^une production // {"headword":"production","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-production
^une exploitation // {"headword":"exploitation","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-exploitation

^un but // {"headword":"but","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^une initialisation // {"headword":"initialisation","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~? **Buts** de l'**initialisation** d'un **projet** :
^comprendre // {"headword":"comprendre","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^un besoin // {"headword":"besoin","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
- **comprendre** les **besoins**
^cadrer // {"headword":"cadrer","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une pratique // {"headword":"pratique","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^techniquement // {"headword":"techniquement","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **cadrer** le projet, par exemple sur le plan des **pratiques** et **techniquement**
^planifier // {"headword":"planifier","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une réalisation // {"headword":"réalisation","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
- **planifier** la **réalisation**
^budgétiser // {"headword":"budgétiser","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **budgétiser**
^rédiger // {"headword":"rédiger","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une proposition commerciale // {"headword":"proposition commerciale","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- rédiger la **proposition commerciale**
^défendre // {"headword":"défendre","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une proposition // {"headword":"proposition","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
- **défendre** cette **proposition**

^un lancement // {"headword":"lancement","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~? **Objectifs** du **lancement** d'un **projet** :
^formaliser // {"headword":"formaliser","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^un cahier des charges // {"headword":"cahier des charges","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-**formaliser**, typiquement **par** le **cahier des charges**
^intégrer // {"headword":"intégrer","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^par exemple // {"headword":"par exemple","category":"other","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^une réflexion non technique // {"headword":"réflexion non technique","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^un marketing // {"headword":"marketing","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-intégrer la **réflexion non technique**, par exemple **marketing**.
-**spécifier fonctionnellement**
^décrire // {"headword":"décrire","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^une interface homme-machine // {"headword":"interface homme-machine","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-décrire les **interfaces homme-machine**
^nécessaire // {"headword":"nécessaire","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-**spécifier techniquement** (en particulier les **performances** nécessaires)

^the phase // {"headword":"phase","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^the project // {"headword":"project","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^typical // {"headword":"typical","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
%# Typical project phases

^the life // {"headword":"life","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
~?**Phases** in the **life of a project**:
-initiation
^kick off // {"headword":"kick off","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-kick-off
^the design // {"headword":"design","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-design
^the production // {"headword":"production","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-production
^the operation // {"headword":"operation","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-operation

^the goal // {"headword":"goal","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the initiation // {"headword":"initiation","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?**Goals** of **project** **initiation**:
^understand // {"headword":"understand","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the need // {"headword":"need","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
- **understand** the **needs**
^frame // {"headword":"frame","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^the practice // {"headword":"practice","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^technically // {"headword":"technically","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **frame** the project, for example in terms of **practices** and **technically**
^plan // {"headword":"plan","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the implementation // {"headword":"implementation","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **plan** the **implementation**
^budget // {"headword":"budget","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **budget**
^draft // {"headword":"draft","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^the commercial proposal // {"headword":"commercial proposal","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- draft the **commercial proposal**
^defend // {"headword":"defend","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the proposal // {"headword":"proposal","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **defend** this **proposal**

^the kick-off // {"headword":"kick-off","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~?**Objectives** of **project** **kick-off**:
^formalize // {"headword":"formalize","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^the requirements specification // {"headword":"requirements specification","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-**formalize**, typically **via** the **requirements specification**
^include // {"headword":"include","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^for example // {"headword":"for example","category":"other","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the non-technical analysis // {"headword":"non-technical analysis","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^the marketing // {"headword":"marketing","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
-include **non‑technical analysis**, for example **marketing**
-**specify functionally**
^describe // {"headword":"describe","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the human–machine interface // {"headword":"human–machine interface","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"C1"}
-describe the **human–machine interfaces**
^required // {"headword":"required","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
-**specify technically** (in particular the required **performance**)

^die Phase // {"headword":"Phase","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
