^一个生命周期 // {"headword":"生命周期","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"shēng mìng zhōu qī","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?项目生命周期中的**阶段**：
- 启动
^启动 // {"headword":"启动","category":"verb","pinyin":"qǐ dòng","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- 立项
^一个设计 // {"headword":"设计","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"shè jì","cefrLevel":"B1"}
- 设计
^一个生产 // {"headword":"生产","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"shēng chǎn","cefrLevel":"B1"}
- 生产
^一个运维 // {"headword":"运维","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"yùn wéi","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- 运维

^一个目的 // {"headword":"目的","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"mù dì","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一个启动 // {"headword":"启动","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"qǐ dòng","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?项目**启动**的**目的**：
^理解 // {"headword":"理解","category":"verb","pinyin":"lǐ jiě","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^一个需求 // {"headword":"需求","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"xū qiú","cefrLevel":"B1"}
- **理解**各方的**需求**
^框定 // {"headword":"框定","category":"verb","pinyin":"kuàng dìng","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^一种实践方式 // {"headword":"实践方式","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"shí jiàn fāng shì","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^技术上 // {"headword":"技术上","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B2","pinyin":"jì shù shang"}
- **框定**项目，例如在**实践方式**和**技术上**加以界定
^规划 // {"headword":"规划","category":"verb","pinyin":"guī huà","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一项实施 // {"headword":"实施","category":"noun","classifier":"项","pinyin":"shí shī","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **规划****实施**
^编制预算 // {"headword":"编制预算","category":"verb","pinyin":"biān zhì yù suàn","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- **编制预算**
^撰写 // {"headword":"撰写","category":"verb","pinyin":"zhuàn xiě","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^一个商务方案 // {"headword":"商务方案","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"shāng wù fāng àn","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- 撰写**商务方案**
^维护 // {"headword":"维护","category":"verb","pinyin":"wéi hù","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一个方案 // {"headword":"方案","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"fāng àn","cefrLevel":"B1"}
- **论证并维护**该**方案**

^一个立项 // {"headword":"立项","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"lì xiàng","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?项目**立项**的**目标**：
^形式化 // {"headword":"形式化","category":"verb","pinyin":"xíng shì huà","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^一份需求说明书 // {"headword":"需求说明书","category":"noun","classifier":"份","pinyin":"xū qiú shuō míng shū","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- 进行**形式化**，典型做法是通过**需求说明书**
^纳入 // {"headword":"纳入","category":"verb","pinyin":"nà rù","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^例如 // {"headword":"例如","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B1","pinyin":"lì rú"}
^一种非技术层面的思考 // {"headword":"非技术层面的思考","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"fēi jì shù céng miàn de sī kǎo","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^一种市场营销 // {"headword":"市场营销","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"shì chǎng yíng xiāo","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- 纳入**非技术层面的思考**，例如**市场营销**等
- 进行**功能性规格说明**
^描述 // {"headword":"描述","category":"verb","pinyin":"miáo shù","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一个人机界面 // {"headword":"人机界面","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"rén jī jiè miàn","cefrLevel":"B2"}
- 描述**人机界面**
^所需 // {"headword":"所需","category":"adjective","pinyin":"suǒ xū","cefrLevel":"B1"}
- 进行**技术性规格说明**（尤其是对所需**性能**的说明）
